WEBVTT

00:40.457 --> 00:43.418
ALL CHARACTERS, PLACES, GROUPS, AND
ORGANIZATIONS IN THIS WORK ARE FICTITIOUS

00:43.501 --> 00:46.379
SCENES WITH ANIMALS ARE STAGED
ACCORDING TO ANIMAL WELFARE GUIDELINES

01:07.484 --> 01:08.568
Grandma!

01:08.651 --> 01:10.278
-Grandma!
-Grandma!

01:10.361 --> 01:11.488
Please stand back.

01:11.571 --> 01:12.572
Grandma!

01:13.865 --> 01:15.658
Grandma.

01:23.541 --> 01:24.876
Grandma.

01:26.336 --> 01:27.378
Grandma…

01:35.845 --> 01:39.891
CURSED HOUSE.
YOU MUST DIE.

01:43.728 --> 01:44.896
What happened?

01:44.979 --> 01:46.648
What's that?

01:46.731 --> 01:48.983
Hey, this is our building!

01:50.693 --> 01:52.570
Which one of you will accompany her?

01:54.322 --> 01:55.365
Excuse me.

01:56.074 --> 01:58.159
All three of us will.

01:58.868 --> 01:59.953
Yeo-reum.

02:02.247 --> 02:03.706
Bom.

02:03.790 --> 02:05.583
What do I do now?

02:06.417 --> 02:07.544
It's okay.

02:08.378 --> 02:09.462
It'll be okay.

02:11.047 --> 02:12.465
He didn't do anything wrong!

02:12.549 --> 02:13.800
-Please!
-Bring him.

02:13.883 --> 02:15.635
-Wait.
-Please move aside.

02:15.718 --> 02:17.679
-Please stand back.
-Wait.

02:22.475 --> 02:23.685
-Please move!
-Hey!

02:23.768 --> 02:25.353
-Hold on. What?
-What happened?

02:25.436 --> 02:27.564
-Geun-ho!
-What's happening?

02:27.647 --> 02:29.357
Geun-ho, it's going to be okay.

02:29.440 --> 02:30.984
Stay calm, okay?

02:31.067 --> 02:31.985
-Don't worry.
-It'll be fine.

02:34.070 --> 02:34.904
No.

02:36.114 --> 02:38.116
She still feels warm.

02:38.867 --> 02:40.201
Grandma.

02:41.953 --> 02:44.122
Grandma, you can't go like this.

02:45.957 --> 02:47.750
Don't go, Grandma.

02:47.834 --> 02:50.795
What do we do now, Grandma?

02:50.879 --> 02:55.174
ANGOK FUNERAL HOME

03:02.181 --> 03:03.933
Let me know if you need more of them.

03:04.017 --> 03:05.059
Okay.

03:05.935 --> 03:08.396
And you can wear this shirt.

03:12.066 --> 03:13.109
Thank you.

03:20.325 --> 03:21.200
Yeo-reum.

03:23.661 --> 03:25.747
Why is life like this?

03:28.541 --> 03:32.295
Why do bad things keep happening?

03:42.555 --> 03:43.723
-Hello.
-Hello.

03:46.226 --> 03:48.102
Bom.

03:48.603 --> 03:49.604
Are you okay?

03:53.566 --> 03:55.235
Yeo-reum.

03:55.318 --> 03:57.779
You need to come with me
to testify as a witness.

03:59.072 --> 04:00.156
Right now?

04:00.657 --> 04:03.868
Yes. We got in touch with Bom's father,

04:03.952 --> 04:05.161
and he'll be here soon.

04:09.332 --> 04:10.291
Then…

04:10.875 --> 04:15.380
could I wait until he gets here?

04:15.964 --> 04:17.006
Yeo-reum.

04:18.049 --> 04:20.051
I'm okay. You can go.

04:26.140 --> 04:27.225
Hey, come on in.

04:28.184 --> 04:29.269
Dae-bum.

04:29.352 --> 04:30.728
What do we do now?

04:32.188 --> 04:33.398
I mean,

04:33.481 --> 04:36.442
I uploaded the thesis on arXiv,

04:37.193 --> 04:38.278
and Holland read it.

04:38.361 --> 04:41.030
Professor Holland read the thesis.

04:41.114 --> 04:42.490
I see.

04:42.573 --> 04:44.200
He wants to talk to us.

04:44.784 --> 04:46.661
We arranged a call for later today.

04:46.744 --> 04:48.246
-Really?
-Yes.

04:49.205 --> 04:52.125
I'm so nervous as to what he'll ask.

04:52.208 --> 04:53.876
-Eun-mi.
-Yes?

04:53.960 --> 04:56.170
Prepare some sample questions, okay?

04:56.254 --> 04:58.131
-All right.
-My goodness.

04:59.340 --> 05:00.258
VIOLENT CRIMES TEAM

05:00.341 --> 05:02.343
How do you know the victim?

05:04.345 --> 05:05.763
I'm close with

05:06.806 --> 05:08.099
her granddaughter.

05:12.061 --> 05:14.272
Why did the victim
visit the billiard club today?

05:17.650 --> 05:20.945
We weren't supposed to meet today.

05:22.947 --> 05:26.617
I've been teaching her Hangeul these days.

05:28.077 --> 05:29.287
Hangeul?

05:33.541 --> 05:35.084
About the guy next door.

05:36.419 --> 05:38.671
Why was Geun-ho there today?

05:39.589 --> 05:40.757
I don't know.

05:42.675 --> 05:44.594
Did he visit the billiard club often?

05:46.846 --> 05:48.347
Not really, but…

05:48.431 --> 05:50.308
Excuse me, Detective.

05:51.184 --> 05:52.977
My kid has

05:53.686 --> 05:56.022
never been to that place.

06:02.111 --> 06:03.654
Geun-ho.

06:03.738 --> 06:06.532
-Geun-ho.
-Geun-ho.

06:06.616 --> 06:08.826
Are you okay, Geun-ho?

06:08.910 --> 06:09.952
Nothing's wrong, right?

06:10.036 --> 06:12.455
-You're not hurt, are you?
-How did it go?

06:13.039 --> 06:14.791
Geun-ho confessed.

06:15.374 --> 06:16.375
What?

06:16.876 --> 06:19.545
-What do you mean?
-That's ridiculous.

06:19.629 --> 06:21.255
Confess to what?

06:21.339 --> 06:25.093
He's already confessed
that he killed the old lady.

06:25.593 --> 06:28.387
-Take him.
-What are you talking about?

06:28.471 --> 06:30.556
He didn't murder anyone!

06:30.640 --> 06:31.599
Geun-ho.

06:31.682 --> 06:32.850
Geun-ho!

06:32.934 --> 06:35.353
-You didn't murder the lady, did you?
-Take him away.

06:35.436 --> 06:37.146
Continue with the investigation.

06:37.230 --> 06:38.439
-Sir.
-Yes, sir.

06:38.523 --> 06:41.400
-He's just lying
-I know you didn't do it, Geun-ho.

06:41.484 --> 06:43.319
because he's afraid of the detectives.

06:43.861 --> 06:45.321
He's just lying.

06:45.404 --> 06:46.948
-Please stand back.
-Stop.

06:47.031 --> 06:49.158
-What's going to happen to Geun-ho now?
-Look at me, Geun-ho.

06:49.242 --> 06:51.452
Stop it!

06:51.536 --> 06:52.954
-Stop it!
-Take him away.

06:53.037 --> 06:55.039
Hold on, Miss.

06:55.123 --> 06:56.582
-Please don't do this.
-Miss.

06:56.666 --> 06:59.377
-My kid was with me at the time.
-Please stop.

06:59.460 --> 07:00.837
He was having a meal with me.

07:00.920 --> 07:02.380
He was with me when it happened.

07:02.463 --> 07:04.924
-Ma'am.
-Can you please tell them that?

07:05.007 --> 07:07.301
-Let's go outside and talk.
-I saw him.

07:08.386 --> 07:09.512
I saw Geun-ho

07:10.596 --> 07:12.306
leave the billiard club.

07:18.229 --> 07:21.107
His clothes were stained red.

07:22.483 --> 07:25.778
At first, I thought it was red paint.

07:29.490 --> 07:31.576
I was rattled, so I ran into the building.

07:33.494 --> 07:34.745
And on the wall…

07:34.829 --> 07:36.247
SLUT. WHORE. DIE. GO AWAY.

07:36.831 --> 07:39.459
There was graffiti everywhere on the wall.

07:39.542 --> 07:40.751
And…

07:42.712 --> 07:44.213
Ms. Jung was lying on the floor.

07:44.881 --> 07:46.090
Ms. Jung.

07:46.174 --> 07:47.175
LEAVE THIS PLACE

07:47.258 --> 07:49.135
Ms. Jung.

07:50.219 --> 07:52.013
Ms. Jung.

07:53.723 --> 07:54.891
Ms. Jung.

07:55.933 --> 07:57.018
Ms. Jung.

07:58.811 --> 07:59.812
Ms. Jung.

08:01.439 --> 08:02.523
Ms. Jung.

08:08.446 --> 08:10.072
Oh, here he is.

08:12.742 --> 08:14.327
It looks like he's hesitating.

08:16.829 --> 08:18.498
That's how he went in.

08:24.003 --> 08:25.421
And here comes Ms. Jung.

08:27.924 --> 08:30.593
He was inside before she arrived.

08:31.802 --> 08:33.804
He was waiting for her to come.

08:35.097 --> 08:37.308
You said he drew
graffiti here before, right?

08:39.644 --> 08:40.728
Yes.

08:41.270 --> 08:44.232
You should have reported him back then.

08:55.201 --> 08:56.244
Ji-yeong.

08:56.786 --> 09:00.748
Bom's grandmother passed away.

09:01.457 --> 09:05.253
She passed away in the billiard club.
They say it was Geun-ho.

09:05.336 --> 09:07.296
I can't believe what's happening here.

10:14.196 --> 10:16.115
-Hello.
-Hey.

10:23.539 --> 10:26.834
The higher-ups are convinced
that he's the culprit.

10:28.836 --> 10:31.505
The CCTV footage shows him
running out from the building

10:31.589 --> 10:33.299
covered in blood.

10:34.133 --> 10:35.968
-Could you help?
-We also have a witness,

10:36.052 --> 10:37.928
-so it's quite conclusive.
-I'll do it.

10:57.698 --> 11:00.117
You. Why didn't you report him before?

11:00.785 --> 11:01.786
Why?

11:02.286 --> 11:05.289
Why didn't you report to the police
about the graffiti?

11:05.790 --> 11:06.916
Sorry?

11:07.500 --> 11:09.418
They said you knew everything.

11:09.502 --> 11:12.505
Why did you call my mom
to your house without even reporting that?

11:12.588 --> 11:14.799
-Why?
-Why are you being like this, Jeong-hun?

11:14.882 --> 11:15.758
I'm sorry.

11:15.841 --> 11:18.427
If you just reported him.
this wouldn't have happened.

11:19.011 --> 11:20.846
That fucking retard murdered my mom.

11:20.930 --> 11:22.181
-That motherfucker…
-Jeong-hun!

11:22.765 --> 11:24.225
-Calm down.
-Dad.

11:24.850 --> 11:26.143
-Hey.
-Dad.

11:26.227 --> 11:27.603
If you just reported him,

11:28.687 --> 11:31.023
if you just said something,
my mom wouldn't have died.

11:31.107 --> 11:32.108
Fuck!

11:32.191 --> 11:33.984
Jeong-hun.

11:34.568 --> 11:37.738
Don't be like that
when you're in mourning for your mother.

11:37.822 --> 11:38.739
I'm sorry.

11:38.823 --> 11:41.200
Hey, this is all your fault.

11:41.283 --> 11:42.827
You killed my mom!

11:42.910 --> 11:45.788
Come on, Dad. She didn't kill her!

11:45.871 --> 11:48.374
Don't you dare come around here.

11:48.457 --> 11:50.418
You better not show your face around here!

11:50.501 --> 11:52.378
Do you hear me?

11:52.461 --> 11:54.255
-Hey.
-Calm down.

11:54.338 --> 11:56.424
-Come by later.
-Get out of here.

11:56.507 --> 11:58.968
-I told you to get out!
-Calm down!

11:59.552 --> 12:00.594
Dad.

12:02.555 --> 12:04.181
-Calm down.
-Dad.

12:04.265 --> 12:06.016
Calm down, okay?

12:15.359 --> 12:16.402
Please.

12:17.611 --> 12:24.618
ANGOK FUNERAL HOME

12:39.800 --> 12:41.719
Don't beat yourself up

12:42.636 --> 12:44.138
over what Holland said.

12:44.221 --> 12:45.389
Even as it is now,

12:46.307 --> 12:48.642
it's worthy of research.

12:50.519 --> 12:52.104
Hawking Radiation.

12:52.771 --> 12:54.940
You can't provide a solution
to that just yet.

12:56.859 --> 12:57.860
Even Holland said

12:58.360 --> 13:00.154
that he doesn't know.

13:01.071 --> 13:02.573
Okay?

13:07.453 --> 13:09.497
JUNG YEONG-SUK
SON: KIM JEONG-HUN

13:09.580 --> 13:11.582
GRANDCHILDREN: KIM BOM, KIM HA-NEUL

13:41.779 --> 13:42.863
Bom.

14:07.721 --> 14:11.600
ANGOK FUNERAL HOME

14:12.434 --> 14:14.144
Hey, you should eat too.

14:14.228 --> 14:15.437
Okay.

14:18.065 --> 14:19.066
What about Bom?

14:20.067 --> 14:21.360
She doesn't want to eat.

14:23.696 --> 14:26.240
She hasn't eaten anything since yesterday.

14:30.244 --> 14:31.495
You got here fast.

14:32.121 --> 14:33.247
No, don't get up.

14:33.330 --> 14:34.582
I'll stay for a bit.

14:36.375 --> 14:38.961
-Then you should eat.
-Later.

14:45.175 --> 14:46.552
I can't believe this happened.

14:53.934 --> 14:56.979
Did you come here directly from Seoul?

14:57.521 --> 14:58.480
Yes.

14:59.148 --> 15:00.441
What about Dae-bum?

15:03.444 --> 15:05.029
Keep this a secret from him.

15:05.821 --> 15:08.449
A secret? Why would you keep it a secret?

15:08.532 --> 15:10.367
He's occupied with an important…

15:12.786 --> 15:14.622
Keep it that way for the time being.

15:15.539 --> 15:16.665
Okay.

15:17.458 --> 15:20.628
I can't contact him anyway
except through you.

15:25.007 --> 15:27.635
I thought Yeo-reum would be here,
but she's not.

15:27.718 --> 15:28.969
Don't even get me started.

15:29.053 --> 15:30.804
Things got really messy.

15:32.097 --> 15:33.223
Why?

15:41.023 --> 15:42.691
I thought she went home.

15:49.907 --> 15:51.533
QUANTUM PHYSICS

16:13.555 --> 16:14.640
Bom.

16:23.273 --> 16:24.650
Bom, my goodness.

16:26.443 --> 16:28.028
This is all too sudden.

16:31.532 --> 16:32.574
I'm sorry.

16:37.663 --> 16:40.165
I only found out
when I went to see you at work.

16:41.166 --> 16:42.251
Bom.

16:43.502 --> 16:44.753
Why are you here?

16:45.462 --> 16:47.172
You should go eat with Bom.

16:51.677 --> 16:53.762
Bom, get up.

16:56.098 --> 16:59.018
Your friend is here. Eat with him.

16:59.601 --> 17:00.644
Get up.

17:03.981 --> 17:05.232
Why are you being like this?

17:20.622 --> 17:22.124
Can you help her so she can eat?

17:23.584 --> 17:26.003
She hasn't eaten anything since yesterday.

17:30.591 --> 17:31.925
Bom.

17:32.009 --> 17:34.470
Your friend is here. Eat.

17:36.013 --> 17:38.015
Please eat something, Bom.

17:40.017 --> 17:41.602
Stop forcing her.

17:43.520 --> 17:46.815
Your grandma hated seeing you skip meals.

17:47.900 --> 17:49.526
Think about how she'd feel

17:49.610 --> 17:51.361
if she were to see you like this.

17:54.948 --> 17:56.867
Are you going to be selfish until the end?

17:58.410 --> 18:00.412
Eat for your grandma, not yourself.

18:30.025 --> 18:30.943
Here.

18:31.527 --> 18:32.569
What's this?

18:32.653 --> 18:35.155
It's a gift for Jun.
I've had it in the car for a while.

18:37.407 --> 18:39.451
Ji-yeong.

18:39.535 --> 18:41.829
The other one is yours.
You haven't slept, right?

18:45.457 --> 18:48.168
Hey, what's with you today?

18:49.086 --> 18:50.462
I just wanted to thank you.

18:51.046 --> 18:52.089
What?

18:53.298 --> 18:55.342
For driving up to Seoul for me…

18:57.010 --> 18:59.179
and for being my friend all this time.

18:59.930 --> 19:01.181
I mean, this is…

19:02.349 --> 19:03.433
Are you okay?

19:03.517 --> 19:07.938
Anyway, I won't treat you
so harshly from now on.

19:09.022 --> 19:10.399
I'll keep it to a minimum.

19:13.527 --> 19:15.404
But you know, people don't change easily.

19:16.405 --> 19:17.447
See you.

19:18.657 --> 19:20.409
Don't get the wrong idea.

19:20.492 --> 19:21.660
I'll end you.

19:28.333 --> 19:29.418
Goodness.

19:32.379 --> 19:33.797
What wrong idea?

19:36.675 --> 19:38.719
Ji-yeong! What wrong idea?

19:38.802 --> 19:39.928
What the…

19:58.030 --> 19:59.948
Get them some more food.

20:00.032 --> 20:01.116
All right.

20:22.846 --> 20:23.931
Jeong-hun.

20:26.099 --> 20:27.684
How dare you show your fucking face here?

20:27.768 --> 20:29.353
-Jeong-hun.
-Get the fuck out.

20:29.436 --> 20:30.812
-How dare you?
-Stop.

20:30.896 --> 20:33.357
-Get out!
-Calm down.

20:33.440 --> 20:35.943
-I'm going to kill him.
-Please calm yourself.

20:36.026 --> 20:39.613
I know you must be heartbroken,
with your mother passing away.

20:39.696 --> 20:40.989
What the fuck did you say?

20:41.073 --> 20:43.242
We know! We know how you feel.

20:43.742 --> 20:44.785
We feel the same way.

20:44.868 --> 20:46.453
-Stop it.
-The hell you do, you pieces of shit!

20:46.536 --> 20:47.537
But!

20:47.621 --> 20:48.997
But please know this.

20:49.581 --> 20:50.707
My Geun-ho…

20:51.416 --> 20:53.043
Geun-ho didn't do it.

20:53.126 --> 20:56.171
-I'm going to kill her.
-Come on, stop.

20:56.255 --> 20:58.382
-Let me go!
-Please believe in me!

20:58.465 --> 21:00.133
Come on, stop it guys.

21:00.217 --> 21:01.718
Please believe me, Jeong-hun.

21:01.802 --> 21:02.803
-Get out!
-Come by later.

21:02.886 --> 21:04.429
-You have no right to be here.
-Get the fuck out of here!

21:04.513 --> 21:06.056
-So just get out!
-Hey!

21:06.139 --> 21:07.182
-Get out!
-Come on.

21:07.266 --> 21:09.893
This is just as hard for us!

21:09.977 --> 21:12.729
-We're barely holding up!
-We know.

21:12.813 --> 21:15.023
I get it. Let's talk outside.

21:15.107 --> 21:17.192
-Hey.
-Come on. Gosh.

21:17.776 --> 21:18.902
Let's talk outside.

21:18.986 --> 21:19.945
-Hey, Seong-min.
-Yes?

21:20.028 --> 21:20.946
Hear me out.

21:21.029 --> 21:24.116
Geun-ho may hurt himself,

21:24.199 --> 21:26.159
but he would never hurt someone else.

21:26.243 --> 21:28.370
How could he have done that to her?

21:28.453 --> 21:31.039
I know, Chang-su.

21:31.123 --> 21:34.042
This is absurd.

21:34.126 --> 21:37.754
But still, you can't come here
and cause a scene!

21:37.838 --> 21:38.839
Why not?

21:38.922 --> 21:40.465
Why can't we?

21:40.549 --> 21:42.968
Our Geun-ho is wrongfully in jail.

21:43.051 --> 21:44.469
How do you think he'll hold up?

21:45.470 --> 21:48.390
What if something bad happens to him?

21:48.473 --> 21:49.308
I get it.

21:49.391 --> 21:51.393
I understand, so let's talk outside.

21:51.476 --> 21:53.937
-Seong-min.
-Chang-su, I get it.

21:54.021 --> 21:55.230
But let's not talk here.

21:55.314 --> 21:58.025
-Let's talk outside.
-This is just so wrong.

21:58.525 --> 21:59.943
They're unbelievable.

22:04.948 --> 22:06.742
-Hello, Professor.
-Did you eat?

22:06.825 --> 22:08.368
Yes. Professor.

22:11.580 --> 22:13.665
Dae-bum is acting strange.

22:13.749 --> 22:15.167
How so?

22:15.751 --> 22:19.046
He kept mumbling
in front of the board all day,

22:19.129 --> 22:21.506
and he suddenly ran to the library.

22:21.590 --> 22:22.591
Really?

22:26.762 --> 22:27.846
Ahn Dae-bum.

22:28.472 --> 22:29.514
Sorry?

22:30.057 --> 22:33.101
Sounds like he found the way
back to his own little black hole.

22:33.727 --> 22:37.189
Let's see what he brings out from there.

22:38.815 --> 22:41.610
-What about Seong-cheol?
-He's taking a break.

22:41.693 --> 22:43.320
Good.

22:43.403 --> 22:44.946
He should be taking a break.

22:45.030 --> 22:45.906
Eun-mi.

22:45.989 --> 22:48.116
Last year's conference files
should be on Seong-cheol's laptop.

22:48.200 --> 22:49.534
Can you send them to me?

22:50.327 --> 22:52.162
I'll text it to you.

22:52.245 --> 22:53.288
Yes, ma'am.

22:53.955 --> 22:55.207
2021 CONFERENCE PRESENTATION

22:55.290 --> 22:57.709
SEND FILE

22:58.418 --> 22:59.628
I sent it.

23:03.173 --> 23:04.299
2021 CONFERENCE PRESENTATION

23:04.382 --> 23:06.426
PROFESSOR LEE

23:07.427 --> 23:10.180
Sir, I've posted it
on the university forums.

23:10.263 --> 23:11.640
Good work.

23:17.229 --> 23:20.982
ANGOK FUNERAL HOME

23:54.724 --> 23:55.851
I'm sorry.

24:02.899 --> 24:03.942
Ms. Jung.

24:09.614 --> 24:10.699
I'm so sorry.

24:34.556 --> 24:35.599
Ms. Jung.

24:37.767 --> 24:39.561
When you get to heaven,

24:40.187 --> 24:43.940
please meet up with my mom.

24:47.402 --> 24:51.823
She would love you.

24:56.203 --> 25:01.416
After my dad passed away,
I asked my mom if she was sad,

25:02.167 --> 25:04.544
and she told me this story.

25:08.590 --> 25:12.302
She told me that life is like
traveling on a bus.

25:14.846 --> 25:16.723
That on this bus of life…

25:18.600 --> 25:21.853
my parents, friends, and acquaintances

25:23.063 --> 25:25.774
are all passengers.

25:27.651 --> 25:29.027
And that one point or another,

25:29.945 --> 25:31.446
they all have to get off.

25:39.412 --> 25:42.707
I sincerely hope you go to a good place

25:42.791 --> 25:44.960
and finally be able to rest in peace.

25:45.502 --> 25:46.544
Okay.

25:47.295 --> 25:49.422
She will go on her final journey now.

25:50.006 --> 25:52.050
Let's wish her a safe journey

25:52.133 --> 25:54.302
with a silent bow.

25:55.220 --> 25:56.429
All bow.

25:58.890 --> 26:02.310
I don't know if my mom
truly believed what she said.

26:05.063 --> 26:08.149
Maybe she had to believe that
to keep herself going.

26:10.360 --> 26:13.530
That parting ways
is a natural part of life.

26:14.155 --> 26:15.282
You may rest.

26:17.909 --> 26:19.244
I'll be closing the door.

26:20.829 --> 26:21.913
Ms. Jung.

26:22.956 --> 26:26.960
Whenever I saw you,
you reminded me of my mom.

26:31.840 --> 26:33.675
I won't forget

26:34.759 --> 26:36.553
everything you did for me.

26:45.687 --> 26:46.771
Ms. Jung.

26:47.772 --> 26:49.065
Goodbye.

26:51.359 --> 26:52.485
Safe travels.

27:07.125 --> 27:08.918
You're home.

27:09.002 --> 27:12.505
I've been waiting for you.

27:12.589 --> 27:15.592
-Can we talk for a bit at my house?
-No.

27:15.675 --> 27:18.261
I have something to give you.

27:18.345 --> 27:21.014
-Please come with me for a minute.
-No, I have nothing to say.

27:21.097 --> 27:22.265
I'm so sorry.

27:22.349 --> 27:24.517
-Why are you being like this?
-Please.

27:24.601 --> 27:27.479
-I won't take much of your time.
-I don't want to.

27:27.562 --> 27:29.606
I'll be really quick.

27:30.398 --> 27:32.776
Come in.

27:33.693 --> 27:35.236
Come on in.

27:35.320 --> 27:36.988
Please have a seat.

27:37.072 --> 27:38.573
What do you want to drink?

27:38.656 --> 27:41.242
Actually, do you want something to eat?

27:41.326 --> 27:43.203
-You're hungry, right?
-No, I'm not.

27:45.080 --> 27:46.122
This.

27:46.748 --> 27:48.500
This is a petition.

27:48.583 --> 27:51.044
Can you please sign one for us?

27:52.629 --> 27:54.214
No, I can't.

27:54.297 --> 27:55.131
Hold on.

27:55.215 --> 27:57.258
Please.

27:57.342 --> 28:00.804
I understand that it may be difficult
for you to sign this.

28:00.887 --> 28:03.223
But please.

28:03.306 --> 28:06.309
I'm grasping at straws here.

28:06.393 --> 28:07.852
When I imagine

28:07.936 --> 28:10.980
my poor son shivering in fear behind bars…

28:11.064 --> 28:12.232
Ma'am.

28:13.066 --> 28:15.985
It's Geun-ho that drew the graffiti
on the building.

28:16.069 --> 28:19.030
But Geun-ho didn't kill anybody.

28:19.114 --> 28:20.657
Stop doing this to me.

28:20.740 --> 28:22.784
Wait! My kid lost
his glasses the day before,

28:22.867 --> 28:25.078
so he wasn't wearing his glasses.

28:25.161 --> 28:27.539
Without glasses, he's practically blind.

28:27.622 --> 28:29.457
How could he have drawn the graffiti?

28:29.541 --> 28:32.752
-Please don't do this.
-Miss, I beg you.

28:32.836 --> 28:36.339
I'm begging you. Please sign this.

28:36.423 --> 28:38.466
Here, sign this.

28:38.550 --> 28:40.301
Do you even hear yourself?

28:41.177 --> 28:43.388
How could you be so selfish?

28:45.014 --> 28:48.184
Bom's grandmother died because of Geun-ho.

28:48.268 --> 28:49.269
That's not true!

28:50.395 --> 28:53.481
When you told me about the graffiti
in the billiard club,

28:54.190 --> 28:55.358
Ms. Jung said

28:56.276 --> 28:58.069
that Geun-ho was a good kid.

28:58.903 --> 29:02.866
And that I shouldn't
report him to the police.

29:02.949 --> 29:06.035
But that Geun-ho went and killed her!

29:06.578 --> 29:07.787
Don't you even feel bad?

29:08.329 --> 29:11.082
How can you only think about your kid?

29:11.666 --> 29:13.710
Geun-ho didn't do it!

29:22.010 --> 29:22.886
Ji-yeong.

29:22.969 --> 29:25.263
-Are you coming from the lab?
-Yes.

29:26.014 --> 29:27.432
You look exhausted.

29:27.932 --> 29:28.933
I'm fine.

29:29.017 --> 29:31.644
Dae-bum hasn't even
been sleeping or eating,

29:31.728 --> 29:33.313
solving problems all day.

29:33.396 --> 29:35.607
Compared to him, I'm not doing much.

29:36.900 --> 29:37.984
I see.

29:41.029 --> 29:42.238
The thing is…

29:42.822 --> 29:44.491
Why do I feel bad?

29:46.117 --> 29:47.535
Why would you?

29:48.411 --> 29:49.496
I called to tell you

29:50.163 --> 29:53.875
that there's going to be
a committee meeting…

29:55.668 --> 29:58.046
and that we need Dae-bum here.

29:58.755 --> 30:00.882
How is that your fault?

30:03.384 --> 30:04.469
Right?

30:05.178 --> 30:06.179
Goodbye, then.

30:07.680 --> 30:08.765
Bye.

30:11.726 --> 30:12.769
Ji-yeong.

30:57.605 --> 30:58.982
Hey, Bom.

31:00.400 --> 31:01.860
And Ha-neul.

31:02.694 --> 31:04.445
Can we talk for a minute?

31:07.866 --> 31:11.035
Bom, I'm sorry.

31:11.661 --> 31:13.997
I'm so sorry.

31:14.080 --> 31:16.082
Ha-neul, I'm sorry.

31:17.333 --> 31:20.295
I've never been a proper dad to you guys.

31:20.378 --> 31:22.797
I apologize for that.

31:23.298 --> 31:26.134
I'm never going to drink again

31:27.093 --> 31:29.470
and I'm only going to live for you.

31:29.554 --> 31:32.473
I'll try my best, so please forgive me.

31:32.557 --> 31:34.767
Please give me one last chance.

31:34.851 --> 31:36.436
I'm sorry.

31:36.519 --> 31:39.606
Get up, Dad.

31:39.689 --> 31:40.690
Gosh.

31:42.025 --> 31:43.026
Hey.

31:43.693 --> 31:46.237
We only have each other now.

31:47.614 --> 31:48.990
With my mom gone too,

31:51.409 --> 31:52.952
you guys are all I have.

31:58.416 --> 31:59.250
Here.

32:04.005 --> 32:06.799
This is condolence money from the funeral.

32:08.134 --> 32:09.844
This will cover our expenses for now.

32:12.472 --> 32:14.349
I'm starting work tomorrow.

32:15.183 --> 32:18.978
I'll be coming home late after work
from now on.

32:21.522 --> 32:22.899
I'll really do my best.

32:24.150 --> 32:26.569
Here, take this. I'll entrust you with it.

32:26.653 --> 32:28.196
Take care of Ha-neul too.

32:31.366 --> 32:32.700
I'm sorry.

32:35.411 --> 32:36.371
Take it.

33:28.214 --> 33:31.509
A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K…

33:38.725 --> 33:42.103
KIM JEONG-HUN

33:42.186 --> 33:45.481
KIM BOM

33:52.280 --> 33:54.532
Grandma…

34:00.288 --> 34:01.414
I miss you.

34:17.263 --> 34:21.142
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

34:34.405 --> 34:36.407
When I first came here,

34:37.200 --> 34:38.242
I had…

34:38.993 --> 34:40.995
nothing left to lose.

34:46.751 --> 34:49.879
I had no idea how to go on…

34:53.424 --> 34:55.384
and my confidence was at rock bottom.

35:15.571 --> 35:16.656
Then…

35:17.490 --> 35:19.325
I made friends in this town.

35:24.080 --> 35:24.997
Bom.

35:26.374 --> 35:27.542
Jae-hun.

35:29.961 --> 35:31.212
Ms. Jung.

35:32.588 --> 35:33.756
Dae-bum.

35:43.975 --> 35:47.436
They helped me smile again.

35:53.192 --> 35:57.363
Every day I spent here was like therapy.

36:08.374 --> 36:09.458
However…

36:10.835 --> 36:13.045
I shouldn't have come here.

36:17.133 --> 36:19.594
If they never met me,

36:22.388 --> 36:26.767
Dae-bum wouldn't have had to
be reminded of this painful past,

36:29.687 --> 36:32.940
and Bom's grandma would have
lived a long and happy life

36:33.524 --> 36:35.818
alongside Bom and Ha-neul.

36:42.617 --> 36:43.618
I never…

36:45.369 --> 36:47.496
should have come to this place.

36:55.004 --> 36:58.132
Let's wrap up
what Dae-bum is looking into for now.

36:58.216 --> 36:59.967
-Okay?
-Yes, sir.

37:00.051 --> 37:01.385
All right.

37:01.469 --> 37:03.721
Let's not go too in-depth.

37:03.804 --> 37:04.805
Hello.

37:05.389 --> 37:06.474
Welcome.

37:12.897 --> 37:14.523
-Professor.
-Yes?

37:15.024 --> 37:17.318
Is it okay to leave Dae-bum like that?

37:17.401 --> 37:18.486
What do you mean?

37:19.070 --> 37:21.697
He's researching without even sleeping.

37:22.782 --> 37:24.492
That's his true side.

37:24.575 --> 37:25.785
I guess you didn't know.

37:26.535 --> 37:28.079
He can't stand not knowing something.

37:28.162 --> 37:29.830
-Eun-mi.
-Yes?

37:31.749 --> 37:34.961
He's gone into his own world.

37:35.044 --> 37:36.295
Just like old times.

37:46.264 --> 37:50.059
Seong-cheol is the one who posted
the accusations on the forum.

37:51.644 --> 37:53.271
Why would Seong-cheol do that?

37:56.190 --> 37:58.317
Professor Lee told him to.

37:58.901 --> 38:02.613
I think Professor Lee asked the dean
to arrange a meeting with Holland

38:02.697 --> 38:05.616
in order for Dae-bum to meet him.

38:06.909 --> 38:07.952
I mean…

38:09.036 --> 38:10.997
What do you mean by that?

38:12.832 --> 38:14.333
What I mean is

38:14.875 --> 38:17.545
Professor Lee is trying to keep
Dae-bum here to have him

38:17.628 --> 38:18.754
write his thesis.

38:25.720 --> 38:27.513
-Ji-yeong.
-Yes?

38:28.097 --> 38:30.558
You'll have to find a place
to stay with Dae-bum.

38:37.148 --> 38:38.190
Yeo-reum.

38:40.568 --> 38:41.861
Gyeo-ul, she's back.

38:43.446 --> 38:44.697
Gyeo-ul.

38:45.281 --> 38:47.033
Come here, Gyeo-ul.

38:47.992 --> 38:49.535
Have you been well?

38:53.289 --> 38:55.750
He's acting like
he hasn't seen you for ages.

38:57.501 --> 38:59.712
Thank you for taking care of him.

38:59.795 --> 39:00.838
It was nothing.

39:03.174 --> 39:04.467
Gyeo-ul.

39:06.135 --> 39:07.094
Yeo-reum.

39:09.180 --> 39:10.806
I might leave this place soon.

39:11.349 --> 39:12.475
What?

39:14.810 --> 39:18.314
My parents want me
back in the States again.

39:21.400 --> 39:23.694
Did you tell Bom?

39:25.946 --> 39:26.989
No.

39:28.074 --> 39:30.951
Bom is going through a lot, so I couldn't.

39:38.959 --> 39:41.087
I'm immature and childish.

39:43.923 --> 39:46.300
So I don't know if I should be beside her.

39:48.677 --> 39:50.388
Yeo-reum.

39:51.263 --> 39:52.348
I'm afraid

39:53.391 --> 39:54.725
that we'll grow apart.

39:55.935 --> 39:57.520
That I'll be forgotten.

40:05.861 --> 40:06.821
Jae-hun.

40:11.325 --> 40:14.578
Just let those growing apart grow apart.

40:15.913 --> 40:17.289
Just let those who hate

40:18.332 --> 40:19.917
hate you.

40:20.668 --> 40:22.002
But as for me,

40:23.003 --> 40:27.883
I'll treat you as my friend
no matter where or when we meet.

40:29.718 --> 40:31.345
When we meet again,

40:32.054 --> 40:34.640
I'll put on a big smile
and give you a hug.

40:36.350 --> 40:38.018
I'll greet you happily.

40:38.102 --> 40:40.521
I'll ask how you fared
and tell you that I missed you.

40:43.607 --> 40:44.733
To me…

40:47.111 --> 40:49.780
you were a good person.

40:51.532 --> 40:52.616
Yeo-reum.

40:55.578 --> 40:56.662
And…

40:57.872 --> 40:59.623
I'm sure Bom thinks that way too.

41:01.250 --> 41:02.293
Yeo-reum.

41:05.921 --> 41:06.922
Thank you.

41:22.396 --> 41:23.439
Hello?

41:24.690 --> 41:25.649
Seong-min.

41:27.109 --> 41:28.569
Are you happy?

41:29.278 --> 41:30.321
What?

41:30.946 --> 41:32.573
What's this out of the blue?

41:32.656 --> 41:34.867
Why am I unhappy when I'm in Seoul?

41:36.702 --> 41:39.872
Hey, is something wrong?

41:42.208 --> 41:44.251
I miss how uneventful it is in Angok.

41:44.335 --> 41:45.169
Gosh.

41:45.252 --> 41:48.672
Uneventful, my foot.
The town is a total mess right now.

41:50.216 --> 41:52.843
Is this about Dae-bum again?

41:54.011 --> 41:56.597
I don't know what to do with him.

41:57.223 --> 42:00.851
Dae-bum must be sad to hear
that Yeo-reum is leaving soon.

42:01.894 --> 42:04.605
-What are you talking about?
-You didn't know?

42:05.481 --> 42:07.566
Yeo-reum is leaving Angok soon.

42:09.360 --> 42:10.361
Hello?

42:10.444 --> 42:12.655
Ji-yeong. Are you there?

42:38.973 --> 42:40.307
It's been a while.

42:44.436 --> 42:45.646
I missed you.

42:54.196 --> 42:55.531
It's hard, right?

42:57.866 --> 42:59.410
Have you eaten?

43:13.215 --> 43:14.300
I'm sorry.

43:23.934 --> 43:26.103
I'm sorry for even apologizing.

43:32.943 --> 43:33.944
Yeo-reum.

43:37.573 --> 43:39.617
I know that it's not your fault,

43:40.909 --> 43:42.453
but I blamed you for it.

43:43.954 --> 43:46.332
I kept telling myself I shouldn't,

43:47.541 --> 43:49.251
but I was so resentful…

43:50.961 --> 43:53.172
because I felt so bad for my poor grandma.

43:55.591 --> 43:57.092
It feels so unfair,

43:58.302 --> 43:59.637
so it makes me furious.

44:00.888 --> 44:03.140
When I try to eat, I get angry.

44:05.225 --> 44:07.436
When I try to sleep, I get angry.

44:08.896 --> 44:10.898
Even just breathing makes me angry.

44:18.030 --> 44:19.156
So…

44:22.701 --> 44:24.203
let's see each other later.

44:25.120 --> 44:26.205
Later.

44:34.505 --> 44:35.506
Okay.

45:26.223 --> 45:27.182
Dae-bum.

45:28.183 --> 45:29.184
Hey.

45:36.316 --> 45:37.609
Let's talk.

45:37.693 --> 45:40.195
Wait, I have to read this part.

45:43.323 --> 45:45.909
Yeo-reum is leaving Angok.

45:49.288 --> 45:50.497
What?

45:52.082 --> 45:55.627
Yeo-reum was involved
in a big incident while you were here.

45:57.838 --> 45:59.631
She hasn't told you, has she?

46:01.341 --> 46:04.303
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

47:27.928 --> 47:29.680
What did Bom's grandma do wrong?

47:29.763 --> 47:32.140
-Why did you kill her?
-Grandma is in danger!

47:32.224 --> 47:33.225
Run away!

47:33.308 --> 47:35.936
Geun-ho has been weighing on my mind.

47:36.019 --> 47:37.813
Look what he drew on the walls.

47:37.896 --> 47:39.022
I told you it's not him.

47:39.106 --> 47:41.984
Could you tell us what this is?

47:42.067 --> 47:44.987
It really sounds like
he's telling me to run away from someone.

47:45.070 --> 47:48.782
I think someone is impersonating
Geun-ho with this graffiti.

47:48.865 --> 47:50.742
Do you think my kid painted this?

47:50.826 --> 47:52.619
My kid who is in jail at the station?

47:52.703 --> 47:54.413
Geun-ho, you didn't kill her, right?

47:54.496 --> 47:55.664
You killed her, didn't you?

47:55.747 --> 47:58.875
Subtitle translation by: Jea-Heon Chung
